ddf685c1-c712-4363-9f83-7849ed7f720f	106dd524-c165-4198-9895-471790e1fe16	aroma	Medium to medium-high rich, deep, sometimes sweet maltiness, with optional qualities such as bread crusts, toast, nuts, cola, dark fruit, or caramel. Roasted malt characters such as chocolate or sweetened coffee can vary from moderate to none but should not overwhelm the base malt character. Low to moderate spicy hop aroma optional. Low diacetyl and low to moderate fruity esters (plums or berries) may be present.	{toast,none,high,optional,spicy,diacetyl,medium,base,deep,aroma}	1	2025-09-27 21:25:58.475468+00
