85576e08-39c2-4f9a-bdc6-88029baa69c8	1d0c766a-cca0-4ee9-aa4d-32e2434a65a1	appearance	Deep yellow to deep gold color; should not have amber hues. Bright clarity. Persistent white to off-white foam stand. Most commercial examples are pale gold in color.	{pale,white,amber,commercial,persistent,hues,foam,color,gold,have}	1	2025-09-27 21:25:58.475468+00
